另一所在德国魏玛，至于荷兰的这个&ldquo;Lizst Junior Academy&rdquo;，网上并没有相关的资料。希望有专业人士不吝赐教。）<br />\n<br />\n巴打拎過咩獎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:00:18.000Z","msg":"又係呢d 要做5星米支連大廚先可以出食評既理論=="},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:22:37.000Z","msg":"冇人話要跑得快過隻馬先可以評<br />\n但評馬人一定有相關的知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f36c738c9766e31cf1da205ed42ba0efa778582","tid":868729,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4a0017caab55ff106aec00f8fe966ed59c2f4f9","tid":868729,"uid":131686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"啲 我的大叔啦 喊撚到七彩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:23:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">睇</span>我的大叔啦 喊到七彩"},{"pid":"7c110fa62e42444364dcb0ac71a2ae0259a066b6","tid":868729,"uid":209609,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T19:26:58.000Z","msg":"我睇完後上網做咗好多research，最後覺得一啲都唔感人。<br />\n唔明點解會有人可以睇到眼濕濕。"},{"pid":"70b6ba3ccf62bc544a9a506e62d301d0abc41bdc","tid":868729,"uid":150230,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T20:22:36.000Z","msg":"四月=神作<br />\n宮園薰真係好女仔...."},{"pid":"b05f2f0bb281bc66274432b5173054ce6ac4e7c6","tid":868729,"uid":12110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T22:06:20.000Z","msg":"近年來睇到有共嗚同感動嘅動畫<br />\n有冇類似嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd oped 幾好聽"},{"pid":"9a3c1499e9d6cb0d7d6a9f07d4f7c1686b6ee43c","tid":868729,"uid":73627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T00:24:05.000Z","msg":"忍唔到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第8 集笑到尾"},{"pid":"88c427196c3d520db8978617f3fdaaf020fbc7f6","tid":868729,"uid":1177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b05f2f0bb281bc66274432b5173054ce6ac4e7c6","tid":868729,"uid":12110,"like":